Name: Trained by a Succubus
About the game: “Trained by a Succubus” is our new Casual game, where you must survive training by a real Succubus. With awesome 2D animation, this is a must play! You will have to survive the training, using your ability to dodge. The sensual Succubus will teach you her arts. Manage your skills wisely if you want to survive her training. You must dodge the dark stars and eat the yellow one, always close to the Heart Button. What you can find in the game: • A challenging enemy that wants to teach you in differents ways. • Beautiful pictures and animations. 17 Scenes and 20 loop animations. • Incredible sound and visual effects.
